      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/criteria/sqa-level5",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2023 R1) is operated under a comprehensive software quality assurance programme conforming to FDA 21 CFR Part 11 and ISO 13485. Version control via Git with mandatory code review, automated regression test suite (1847 tests, 100% pass rate), validated installation qualification (IQ) and operational qualification (OQ) records on the HPC cluster, and traceability matrix linking each solver capability to test cases. All simulation scripts are version-controlled and archived with cryptographic hash verification. SQA level 5 achieved."
